Package com.kuka.roboticsAPI.applicationModel

Contains classes needed for applications using RoboticsAPI.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IApplicationControl Interface for application controls.
IApplicationData Interface for application data.
IApplicationOverrideControl Interface for application override control.
IApplicationOverrideListener Interface for an application override listener.
IRoboticsAPIApplication RoboticsAPI application interface.
 

Class Summary
RoboticsAPIApplication Base class for RoboticsAPI applications.
RoboticsAPIApplicationControl Class to get an robotics API application control.
RoboticsAPIApplicationData Class to get a robotics API application data.
RoboticsAPIOverrideControl Class to get control robotics API overrides.
RoboticsAPIProgramPart Base class for classes that need access to the RoboticsAPIContext and resources provided by the context, such as persistent data.
 

Enum Summary
RoboticsAPIApplicationState RoboticsAPI application state changed events.
